drop table "CON_Partner" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "CON_Partner" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_Partner"
(
"PartnerID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ContractID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"SAPContractCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"CompanyID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CompanyCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"EntityID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"EntityCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"RoleType" VARCHAR(10) not null,
BPID NUMBER(32) not null,
"BPCode" VARCHAR2(50) not null,
"BPName" NVARCHAR2(200) not null,
"BPCertificate" VARCHAR2(30) not null,
"RegisteredAddress" NVARCHAR2(200),
"RepName" NVARCHAR2(50),
"RepContactTel" NVARCHAR2(50),
"ContactAddress" NVARCHAR2(200),
"ContactName" NVARCHAR2(100),
"ContactTel" NVARCHAR2(50),
"EntrustName" NVARCHAR2(100),
"EntrusIDNum" NVARCHAR2(50),
constraint PK_CON_PARTNER primary key ("PartnerID")
);

comment on column "CON_Partner"."RoleType" is
'对应SAP的ROLE_TYPE Z001是承租方，Z099是授权方
';

comment on column "CON_Partner".BPID is
'记录经销商ID';

comment on column "CON_Partner"."BPCode" is
'对应MD_Dealer内的DealerCode';
